Package: MSSI
Title: The multiscale straightness index for the analysis of animal trajectories
Version: 0.1
Author: Frank Pennekamp <Frank.Pennekamp@posteo.de>
Maintainer: Frank Pennekamp <Frank.Pennekamp@posteo.de>
Description: This R package contains two functions to calculate the MSSI for a
    given trajectory and then plot the measure and the associated trajectory.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Imports:
    zoo,
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    tcltk,
    gridExtra
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    knitr
